# Data Source: tfe_scim_group

Use this data source to read a SCIM group that has been synchronized from the configured Identity Provider into Terraform Enterprise. It applies only to Terraform Enterprise and requires admin token configuration. See example usage for incorporating an admin token in your provider config.

Use `name` to look up a single group by its exact display name (case-insensitive). The data source filters out fuzzy substring matches returned by the API and keeps only exact matches.

